    %% Flows
    DSPO -.->|deploys & configures<br/>no network traffic| WFC
    DSPServer -->|HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token<br/>Submit Workflow CR| K8sAPI

    K8sAPI -->|Watch notification<br/>HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token| WFC
    WFC -->|HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token<br/>Create/Manage Pods| K8sAPI

    WFC -->|creates Pods with| ArgoExec
    ArgoExec -->|HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token<br/>Get WF, Patch annotations| K8sAPI
    ArgoExec -->|HTTPS or HTTP<br/>443 or 9000/TCP<br/>TLS configurable<br/>Access Key| S3

    WFC -->|TCP/5432<br/>TLS configurable<br/>Username/Password<br/>Archive workflows| PostgreSQL

    Prometheus -->|HTTP/9090<br/>plaintext<br/>no auth<br/>Scrape /metrics| WFC_Metrics

